@page "/"

<PageTitle>CoderBash.Net.Vies - EU VAT Services</PageTitle>

<h1>EU VAT Services</h1>

<p>Welcome to the CoderBash.Net.Vies Blazor UI!</p>

<p>This application provides access to EU VAT validation and VAT rate information services:</p>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">VAT Number Validation</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Validate VAT numbers using the official VIES (VAT Information Exchange System) service from the European Commission.</p>
                <a href="/vat-validation" class="btn btn-primary">Validate VAT Number</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">VAT Rates</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Look up current VAT rates for all EU member states including standard, reduced, and super-reduced rates.</p>
                <a href="/vat-rates" class="btn btn-primary">View VAT Rates</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
